            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "曼聯│歐霸決賽前收到好消息 剋星熱刺鋒將古路施夫斯基未傷瘉難上陣",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"歐霸決賽前收到好消息，剋星熱刺鋒將古路施夫斯基未傷瘉難上陣。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bb7268ea128ba2165c172ef862c4c6f7/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250514/_2025051418453940398.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">歐霸決賽前收到好消息，剋星熱刺鋒將古路施夫斯基未傷瘉難上陣。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>曼聯下周三與熱刺爭奪歐霸冠軍，他們在周二收到好消息，今季3次交手入2球的熱刺攻擊主力古路施夫斯基(Dejan Kulusevski)，因膝傷比預期嚴重難趕及上陣，紅魔守將可望鬆一口氣。\n\n</p><h2>古路施夫斯基膝傷比預期嚴重</h2>\n<p>今季各賽事收錄10球11助攻的古路施夫斯基，剛輪英超主場0:2不敵水晶宮時，正選披甲僅19分鐘就撞傷膝蓋退下火線，領隊普斯迪高古賽後曾表示其傷勢不嚴重，只是撞傷。然而《曼徹斯特晚報》周二報導，這名瑞典鋒將的膝傷比預期嚴重，經檢查後隊醫認為難趕及在下周三歐霸上陣，與另一攻擊主力占士麥迪臣一起高掛免戰牌。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古路施夫斯基上周對水晶宮時受傷。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3eae0212ba24fe4611e87a86c300b15f/2025-05/1_36.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古路施夫斯基上周對水晶宮時受傷。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古路施夫斯基撞傷膝蓋。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8a6b31dd891cc1108232f63982c1a861/2025-05/2_0_10.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古路施夫斯基撞傷膝蓋。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古路施夫斯基料未能趕及在歐霸決賽復出。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/97c7ef352ff451319cbcd3d68a8132be/2025-05/3_35.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古路施夫斯基料未能趕及在歐霸決賽復出。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古路施夫斯基於19分鐘就被換走。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/72f6514f5d75a4ae178021befe7a4bc9/2025-05/4_30.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古路施夫斯基於19分鐘就被換走。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古路施夫斯基今季英超首循環大勝曼聯時，曾攻入1球。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/39e940067fd475b42c01fe9847845e97/2025-05/5_28.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古路施夫斯基今季英超首循環大勝曼聯時，曾攻入1球。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古路施夫斯基今季英超首循環大勝曼聯時，曾攻入1球。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c831c328087245f028c8721b8e16b6b7/2025-05/6_14.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古路施夫斯基今季英超首循環大勝曼聯時，曾攻入1球。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古路施夫斯基今季對曼聯表現出色。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2e44444bb5093669a70ec314bba90d0b/2025-05/7_22.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古路施夫斯基今季對曼聯表現出色。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"去年12月聯賽盃8強，古路施夫斯基入1球助熱刺淘汰曼聯。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/02799a4ddf84fc7aa4ee9f392a3f242d/2025-05/8_13.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        去年12月聯賽盃8強，古路施夫斯基入1球助熱刺淘汰曼聯。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古路施夫斯基今季各賽事3次對曼聯入2球。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb48668773f1ed7194671f9475d60a1f/2025-05/9_10.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古路施夫斯基今季各賽事3次對曼聯入2球。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古路施夫斯基今季對曼聯屢有佳作。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4f60fefca7a7438df59bc2ba84b3d7b9/2025-05/10_12.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古路施夫斯基今季對曼聯屢有佳作。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古路施夫斯基是曼聯的剋星。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/17b1bd1d746049c4f2c7ff756b1a4ae8/2025-05/11_6.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古路施夫斯基是曼聯的剋星。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>今季3對曼聯入2球</h2>\n<p>紅魔守將聽到這消息可望鬆一口氣，事緣古路施夫斯基今季各賽事3次對曼聯攻入2球，領軍在這3仗全勝，如今大有機會倦勤，球隊贏波機會大減。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
