        {
            "title": "上水河上鄉單車男捱撞  受傷倒卧地上",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"傷者倒卧地上。fb： 香港公共交通智庫\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/699d5101e550101eda3c1a8712a6d76c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250514/_2025051418223036542.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">傷者倒卧地上。fb： 香港公共交通智庫</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（14日）傍晚5時46分，一輛私家車沿青山公路行駛，馳至河上鄉對開，撞倒一部單車，頓時人車分離，男子飛墮地上，由救護車送院治理。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4248559/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"傷者倒卧地上。fb： 香港公共交通智庫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/809fe8f19bf6e39fa83487ec6b977b9a/2025-05/01_0_26.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        傷者倒卧地上。fb： 香港公共交通智庫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4248560/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"青山公路發生交通事故。fb： 香港公共交通智庫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c4fc820c9aa88ded68f4ba1524d0bc50/2025-05/02_1_13.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        青山公路發生交通事故。fb： 香港公共交通智庫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
